==Gothic==
===Etymology===
From common Germanic '''[[*hundaz]]''', from Proto-Indo-European '''[[*岣眞n胎t贸s]]''', derived from '''[[*岣眞艒]]''', "dog". Near cognates include Old English ''[[hund]]'', Old Icelandic ''[[hundr]]'', and Old High German ''[[hunt]]''.


